{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u27a4 Explore a Breathtaking and Alien World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Isle of Ardenfall is a diverse landscape of windy plains, flooded wetlands, ancient ruins, and winding caves. As you explore the compact open world and deep dark dungeons you will discover countless secrets, dangerous monsters, and interesting characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154960/extras/gif_world.gif?t=1738342702\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u27a4 Create your Character Your Own Way</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How you craft your character will have long term consequences - choose your character\u2019s race, tattoos, attributes, traits,  and more. These decisions will unlock dialog options, alter your strengths and weaknesses, and even define how others trust (or distrust) your character! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154960/extras/gif_traveler_fast.gif?t=1738342702\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u27a4 Defeat Your Foes With Sandbox Combat Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your weapon. Now choose another. If you are stuck, there\u2019s always more options to get you out of a bind - a throwing potion, a single use spell, or a throwing knife of fire may do the trick. A mage specialized in summoning may spawn a great beast to do their bidding, while a thief may toss a potion of silence on their targets to ensure a clean kill. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154960/extras/sandbox-combat.gif?t=1738342702\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u27a4 Make Your Mark on a Changing World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you complete quests and join various factions, your decisions will effect the world of Ardenfall. Economics of regions will shift at the swing of your blade, and the citizens will remember your decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154960/extras/make-your-mark.gif?t=1738342702\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u27a4Meet Countless Interesting Characters </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Interact with a unique range of characters across the world, each with different perspectives, beliefs, and culture. Building trust with the people of Ardenfall unlocks new paths in your journey - you may however need to charm, convince or lie to get what you desire. </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154960/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738342702","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154960/page.bg.jpg?t=1738342702","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154960/130986085480081d7e44e13bed3e1cd90220452a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738342702","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154960/130986085480081d7e44e13bed3e1cd90220452a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738342702","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Stats","id":15}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":1837770,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u27a4 Explore a Breathtaking and Alien World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Isle of Ardenfall is a diverse landscape of windy plains, flooded wetlands, ancient ruins, and winding caves. As you explore the compact open world and deep dark dungeons you will discover countless secrets, dangerous monsters, and interesting characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam